The next MO VINO of the season will be on Thursday March th The last MO VINO was very well attended so make sure you get your email in soon Also note that Tim Williams will be providing us with the entertainment and the cover to hang around for him is an extra It is well worth the extra money we are very lucky to have Tim in the Double MO and his show is always great The cost for MO VINO is per person which includes tastings of eight wines a variety of cheeses french baguette and your programme If you are interested in attending please send an email and let us know how many people are attending We get started at SharpNOTE EARLIER START Remember the DOUBLE MO is licensed but nonsmoking Check out the DOUBLE MO website at wwwdoublemocom for all the music listings and other information about the cafe Look forward to seeing you at these and other events at the Double MO Cheers Alaina PS The DOUBLE MO Cafe is located in the Stadium Shopping Centre at Uxbridge Drive NW For more info call us at You are receiving this email because you are a valued Customer of the DOUBLE MO Caf or you are a friend of Alaina If you would like to change your email address or know someone else who
